in the Central Plains.

574
00:40:21,956 --> 00:40:22,636
By then,

575
00:40:23,115 --> 00:40:24,436
he will be like a street dog,

576
00:40:24,436 --> 00:40:25,196
with nothing.

577
00:40:25,755 --> 00:40:26,515
What should I do?

578
00:40:27,156 --> 00:40:27,716
Follow him

579
00:40:28,236 --> 00:40:29,476
and become a street dog

580
00:40:29,476 --> 00:40:30,476
with nothing?

581
00:40:30,916 --> 00:40:32,355
As long as you are willing to help him,

582
00:40:33,035 --> 00:40:34,196
he can stay in the Central Plains

583
00:40:34,196 --> 00:40:35,075
and turn the tide.

584
00:40:35,476 --> 00:40:35,916
Xinyue,

585
00:40:36,835 --> 00:40:38,355
