586
00:40:38,355 --> 00:40:39,795
and not take any risks.

587
00:40:40,315 --> 00:40:41,676
There is no such thing as a free lunch.

588
00:40:42,716 --> 00:40:43,876
What is he to me?

589
00:40:44,075 --> 00:40:45,275
What has he done for me?

590
00:40:45,795 --> 00:40:47,716
Why should I take risks for him?

591
00:40:48,396 --> 00:40:48,835
Anyway,

592
00:40:49,916 --> 00:40:51,156
