593
00:40:52,196 --> 00:40:53,355
I will definitely not do so.

594
00:41:04,156 --> 00:41:04,755
Cang Xuan.

595
00:41:04,996 --> 00:41:05,636
Fenglong,

596
00:41:06,275 --> 00:41:07,876
I've carefully considered your proposal.

597
00:41:08,876 --> 00:41:10,236
But now I can hardly protect myself,

598
00:41:10,676 --> 00:41:12,196
so I'm not a good match for Xinyue.

599
00:41:13,315 --> 00:41:14,156
Let's forget about

600
00:41:14,755 --> 00:41:15,595
the marriage.

601
00:41:17,555 --> 00:41:18,515
But I appreciate

602
00:41:19,956 --> 00:41:20,835
your good intentions.

603
00:41:36,595 --> 00:41:37,396
Cang Xuan,

604
00:41:38,196 --> 00:41:39,275
about the marriage proposal,

605
00:41:39,595 --> 00:41:40,716
